originalText.text: I was very nervous entering the bankruptcy process. I didn't have any idea what to expect and was apprehensive about following through. Mr Farinella made me feel comfortable and relaxed from the very beginning. He answered any questions I had in a timely manner as well as kept me updated on any information I needed to know. He was reassuring and eliminated all my worries. He and all his staff were professional, patient, informative and kind I would recommend them to my family and friends.I give the team a 10 out of 10. Thank you so much for your expertise. Now I'm off to a brand new start
